    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Chainwarden artillerists are the siege specialists of the Warden companies — trained crossbowmen who carry heavy arbalests and satchels of alchemical munitions. Their Alchemical Bolt can set targets ablaze, and their Covering Fire suppresses entire zones of the battlefield. Deployed in platoons behind the infantry line, they can rain fiery bolts from range while the melee holds the enemy in place.</p>",
